VASSAL.build.module.documentation

Class HelpFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • VASSAL.build.AbstractBuildable
      • VASSAL.build.AbstractConfigurable
        • VASSAL.build.module.documentation.HelpFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoConfigurable, Buildable, Configurable, PropertyNameSource, ValidityChecker, Translatable

    public class HelpFile
extends AbstractConfigurable
    Places an entry in the Help menu. Selecting the entry displays a window with stored text on it.
